name: MiniChillas
description: 1369 Digital Chinchillas exploring the MiniVerse looking for frens or foes. Chillas are Genesis MiniVerse Finance NFT's and earn MvDOLLAR(algorithmic stable coin pegged of 1:1 USDC) by staking. Through utilizing MvDOLLAR in our NFT GameFi, holders will be able to earn rewards/prizes, breed the next generation, and much more!
